Class TTManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.endeavourhealth.informationmanager.common.transform.TTManager

  • public class TTManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Various utility functions to support triple tree concepts and documents. Create document creates a document with default common prefixes.
